{"tid":1932991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"桃園機場入境要排逾4小時　萬人逃難返台！！！","createTime":"2020-03-19T04:55:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T15:38:04.000Z","uid":209657,"like":92,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"84e3a2616abfef29a87dcb2f42f21d7fad1021c2","tid":1932991,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:55:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/03/18/3104440_2_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F03%2F18%2F3104440_2_1.jpg&h=0c585a10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n19日起外籍旅客限制入境，再加上加拿大封城，美國也列入3級疫區，很多遊子急著趕回台灣，預期將湧現歐洲、美、加返國人潮；不過，桃園機場檢疫通關也大排長龍，今天傍晚5點落地的旅客至少要花4小時才能通過檢疫通道，不少旅客質疑擁擠人潮恐怕會成為感染的大溫床。"},{"pid":"cb01df17f8682b4a5c22115a7f9e34f0ab3b1879","tid":1932991,"uid":209657,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:56:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/03/18/realtime/7615451.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=930&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F03%2F18%2Frealtime%2F7615451.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D930%26nt%3D1&h=6b75d902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現行檢疫規定，從列為第3級旅遊警示地點入境的旅客，必須執行居家檢疫14天，其他地區入境也要執行自主健康管理，雖然18日桃園機場預報入境人數僅9000餘人，但只要同時有2班以上的飛機抵達，入境檢疫站前旅客就會排長龍，衛福部疾管署派出所有的人力審核文件，速度還是快不起來，需要花費2、3個小時以上才能消化所有人龍。<br />\n<br />\n18日清晨桃園機場第2航廈同時有多班美國線班機抵達，入境旅客排隊長度就超過了好幾個候機室長度。下午第1航廈也出現相同情形，排隊人龍超過100公尺，部分旅客抱怨等候太久。"},{"pid":"ba97fd6649a48897ab5da026aa2eaa039a2017f0","tid":1932991,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:57:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3104440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3104440&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzOzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=0095eb29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3104440&h=afee2f31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3104440</a><br />\n有片"},{"pid":"688f9e73ccff2a8594c23863a1a626737f17df23","tid":1932991,"uid":209657,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4765/d4765883.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4765%2Fd4765883.jpg&h=7a74dfe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n交通部長林佳龍指出，由於歐美等國疫情嚴峻，預期許多旅外台灣人，會趁這兩天趕回台灣，據估單今天就會有1萬人返台，且皆須居家檢疫。實際上看數據，今日預報有8881人返台，明日有9000人以上，有立委指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">海外留學生多達7萬人</span>，預估都會搶在近日趕回台灣，搭車人數暴增10倍。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日桃園機場現場，就有許多返國民眾耗費很多時間在等搭車，排隊人潮大排長龍。據了解，除了人潮多之外，主要是因為防疫車隊搭乘時有嚴格SOP，包含要登記名單造冊、確認檢疫通知單，還得要行李消毒、手部消毒等。"},{"pid":"2e318f1aaa196012b071cc6c62d5633f8e02b032","tid":1932991,"uid":25858,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:59:09.000Z","msg":"梗係要等下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b70b02e7f999a7bf6f143b14147f52852255fd50","tid":1932991,"uid":1159,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:59:25.000Z","msg":"留名等睇連登仔屌台灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a9d3edf61b6f4189e7b0923ab0a50495adfd4d","tid":1932991,"uid":209657,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T05:00:16.000Z","msg":"黃良易說，旅客排隊人潮湧現，人潮最多時，旅客需要等待超過1個多小時才可以上車。<br />\n<br />\n入面排三個鐘，外面又排"},{"pid":"43d1aa33df4de18a769c62cad443e86dfc10ae82","tid":1932991,"uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"84e3a2616abfef29a87dcb2f42f21d7fad1021c2","tid":1932991,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03